///Components Used:
1. Arduino Uno
2. Ultrasonic Sensor
3. Servo Motor
4. Breadboard
5. Jumper Wires


///Circuit Connection Details:

   #  Ultrasonic Sensor to Arduino:
Trigger Pin: Connects to Digital Pin 6 on the Arduino.
Echo Pin: Connects to Digital Pin 7 on the Arduino.
Vcc: Connects to 5V on the Arduino.
Gnd: Connects to Gnd on the Arduino.
Servo Motor to Arduino:
Control Signal (Orange wire): Connects to Digital Pin 9 on the Arduino.
Vcc (Red wire): Connects to 5V on the Arduino.
GND of Servo Motor (Black) to GND
